    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the single-load-configuration limitation of ASTM F1717 and is accepted given corroborating analytical evidence and the medium model risk level. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
